Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也加入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？你也是同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  大家都要玩這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修哉也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修哉不喜歡和姐姐不一樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事沒…又好像有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過就沒有敵人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了啊  塗鴉戰隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:04:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:04:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  我是怪人眼鏡大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字好土
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧  你也變身和我們一起戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要讓這傢伙也戴上眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會讓你得逞的！站住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點跟上來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  蕾說的是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電話裡說爸爸媽媽被捲進坍方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有找到媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受夠了  為什麼總是我們遭這樣的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以為好不容易能夠變得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  大家都不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的房間還沒關門？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次偷偷溜進去還被罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還沒鎖上  應該行的吧
